{"tid":1165990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【收衫墮樓】男童留院治理傷勢樂觀 母親對被捕感無奈","createTime":"2019-05-22T07:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T09:47:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"97ecf16b113da3f52ca979bf4262a4d2e78e6b6b","tid":1165990,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:05:15.000Z","msg":"患過度活躍症的12歲姓鄭男童，昨晨在荃灣劏房住所收衫時墮樓致腳部骨折，情況一度危殆，經醫生搶救後，情況終漸穩定下來。鄭母稱，兒子腳傷已打石膏，肋骨的骨裂有待時間癒合，總算讓她放下心頭大石，又謂新屋已經安裝窗花，並會用鎖頭鎖起；至於鄭母自己因兒子墮樓被捕及有可能被警方檢控疏忽照顧，她只感到無奈。<br />\n鄭母（42歲）稱，長子在內地出世，1歲左右已經移居香港。「好細個已經發現佢同其他小朋友唔同，比較活躍。喺深圳睇過醫生，話佢無事；最終喺香港再排到隊，（醫生）確診有過度活躍。」<br />\n鄭母續稱，長子小時候比較百厭，「大大吓定咗，現在好少亂嚟」。兒子半年前因為胃痛，停止服食過度活躍症的藥物，醫生也知道，現時仍需定期覆診。<br />\n她相信今次墮樓意外與兒子的過度活躍症無關，「佢唔鍾意同細佬一齊返學，鍾意自己返，又堅持要穿着運動服」，墮樓後他痛極呼救，驚動街坊報警。現場所見，窗戶離地約4呎，床架約2呎高，鄭童站在床上俯身收衫，確實很危險。<br />\n現時鄭童右小腿骨折已打石膏，稍後會安排做手術，至於腰間兩條肋骨骨裂，則有待癒合，幸醫生表示情況樂觀。<br />\n對於因涉嫌疏忽照顧兒童，鄭母已被警方拘捕，更有機會被落案刑事檢控，她表示無奈：「無辦法啦！佢大個仔，唔肯跟你返學、跟你出街，唔留喺屋企，留喺邊度呀？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190522/large/1558506094_0fe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190522%2Flarge%2F1558506094_0fe3.jpg&h=5c01393b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190522/59627790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190522%2F59627790&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=e3ffc36a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190522%2F59627790&h=d33ad1f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190522/59627790</a>"},{"pid":"53c6b785cda37819343fc6187945e2991a928d4c","tid":1165990,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"點解會要個4歲小朋友收衫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有病"},{"pid":"770deba9fffb9f91b1409bd82f3f1e3b73e108f5","tid":1165990,"uid":228963,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30dfe9cae23b3fa07798d813c9119a0a6dcadd88","tid":1165990,"uid":14103,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:09:43.000Z","msg":"原來係大陸狗"},{"pid":"21b8560cb690b1c386688836f08391126f5b22a7","tid":1165990,"uid":45773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"53c6b785cda37819343fc6187945e2991a928d4c","tid":1165990,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"點解會要個4歲小朋友收衫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有病"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:12:13.000Z","msg":"認知障礙？"},{"pid":"52349a218a1ee10619a8dc67789dabe1e3581f5b","tid":1165990,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53c6b785cda37819343fc6187945e2991a928d4c","tid":1165990,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"點解會要個4歲小朋友收衫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有病"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:12:22.000Z","msg":"患過度活躍症的12歲姓鄭男童，昨晨在荃灣劏房住所收衫時墮樓致腳部骨折～ 邊度四歲？～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58dfc6946e2820e5a5249884d0651505abb68bb0","tid":1165990,"uid":147721,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"53c6b785cda37819343fc6187945e2991a928d4c","tid":1165990,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"點解會要個4歲小朋友收衫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有病"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"四樓呀四歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54af9829270cc0e54b11c553088e5da5d40ed2c1","tid":1165990,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,